Score each ranking like follows using 64 bits

Royal Flush (just for fun):
10 00 00 00 00 00

Straight flushes:
9 00 00 00 00 00

Four of a kind:
8 00 00 00 00 00

Full house:
7 00 00 00 00 00 

Flush:
6 00 00 00 00 00

Straight:
5 00 00 00 00 00

Three of a kind:
4 00 00 00 00 00

Two pairs:
3 00 00 00 00 00

One pair:
2 00 00 00 00 00

High cards:
1 00 00 00 00 00

The strength of the hands would be encoded in each two digits.
